{"tid":2217338,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"據悉部分被捕港人家屬向深圳公安申請「取保候審」","createTime":"2020-09-25T10:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T13:35:07.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3c23e324b4deedb9b4d1b27dd337affefbc2f71d","tid":2217338,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:58:18.000Z","msg":"據了解，12名港人被刑事拘留在深圳的事件，部分當事人的家屬，已經向深圳市公安鹽田分局申請「取保候審」，即是類似保釋的手續，預料其餘家屬會陸續申請。<br />\n<br />\n有家屬接受本台訪問時表示，對於成功獲批「取保候審」的信心不大，但仍然提出申請，是因為距離37天刑事拘留的限期快將屆滿，希望內地當局知道家屬和港人都仍然關注事件，希望當局下每一個決定時要審慎處理。<br />\n<br />\n這名家屬說，是透過香港入境處的「協助在外香港居民小組」向內地當局提出申請，但暫時仍未收到入境處回覆是否己將取保文件轉交內地。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，當事人成功獲批的話，提交保證金或者擔保人簽字，便可以離開看守所，但需要交出旅遊證件，不能離開內地。有內地律師認為，根據以往經驗，內地「取保」成功率不高，只有大約2%至3%，加上這次案件敏感，預料獲批的機會非常低。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551660-20200925.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551660-20200925.htm&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwzkwAUq3ZsepC89uAf1Ef2WI%3D&h=119086b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551660-20200925.htm&h=fd2aa06c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551660-20200925.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1da4fec7bc2e6c085f35c3dbcd112f8a1074fb88","tid":2217338,"uid":78947,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T10:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d56cd4d088f605c0d1f528a7eb0876c865fe4e75","tid":2217338,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:12:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324bb2c9b811f89353f12df7fd67cc34e31b7fef","tid":2217338,"uid":66049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:25:18.000Z","msg":"入境狗應該已經將啲文件扔咗落垃圾桶啦"},{"pid":"5e35555f39efed6f9e6b313d3baaaf8f25a7124e","tid":2217338,"uid":354682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T11:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb15b89cc080615da7ede89ae162c505ef6d0db","tid":2217338,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T13:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}